This is a simple video player, that displays a rss feed scrolling at screen bottom, created with Processing.

==========Dependencies==========
You need to install Processing (http://processing.org/download/).
You need to add GSVideo (http://gsvideo.sourceforge.net/).

==========Configuration==========
You can set video folder and max itens by feed in VideoPlusRSS.pde.
See default values:

//==============================================

//Set you moovies folder
moviesFolder=dataPath("movies");

//Set Max itens by feed
maxItens=10;

//==============================================


URL Feeds can be set at: VideoPlusRSS/data/feeds.config
